Name: Ferran Torres
Number: 19
Position: Forward
Goals: 2
Assists: 2

He brings together various talents which allow him to operate anywhere up front.
Born on 29 February 2000 in Foios (Valencia), Ferran Torres made first contact with 
the ball at an early age. He started out with futsal at the EPLA school and then 
attracted the attention of the Valencia CF academy. He was only seven years when he 
wore the shirt for the first time.
